## 2. INFORMATION WE COLLECT

### 2.1 Data Stored Locally on Your Device (We Do NOT Have Access)

The following data is stored **exclusively on your device** using local storage:

**Session Data:**
- Date and time of each session
- Duration and technique used (breathing, grounding, distraction)
- Panic intensity ratings (if you provide them)
- Notes or journal entries (if you add them)
- Effectiveness ratings
- Calendar history and progress statistics

**App Settings:**
- Theme preference
- Haptic feedback setting
- Other app preferences

**Emergency Contact (Optional):**
- Contact name and phone number (if you choose to add one)
- Pre-written message
- **Important:** This information stays on your device. We never receive or have access to it.

**Disclaimer Acceptance:**
- A flag indicating you accepted the medical disclaimer
- Timestamp of acceptance

**What This Means:**
- We do NOT receive copies of this data
- We do NOT have access to your session details
- We CANNOT see your panic attack history
- This data is NOT backed up to cloud servers
- If you delete the app or lose your device, this data is lost
- You have complete control over this data

