## 6. DATA RETENTION

### 6.1 Retention Periods

**Local Data (On Your Device):**
- Stored indefinitely on your device
- Deleted when you delete the app or clear app data
- We cannot delete it (we don't have access to it)

**Subscription Records:**
- Transaction records: 7-10 years (required by tax law)
- Anonymous subscription status: 90 days after cancellation

**Support Communications (if you contact us):**
- 3 years

### 6.2 Deleting Your Data

**To delete local data:**
- Delete the Anchor Me app from your device
- Or: Settings > General > iPhone Storage > Anchor Me > Delete App

**To cancel subscription:**
- Managed through Apple: Settings > Your Name > Subscriptions
- Or through RevenueCat's customer portal

**Note:** Canceling your subscription does not delete local data from your device.

